\c 3
\s Mwari ndiye murwiri panjodzi
\s Pisarema raDhavhidhi panguva
\s yokutiza kwake Abhusaromu mwanakoâ€‘
\s mana wake.
\p
\v 1 Haiwa Jehovha, vadzivisi vangu vawanda sei! Vazhinji vanondirnukira.
\v 2 Vazhinji variko vanoti kumweya wangu, "Haano ruponeso kuna Mwari."
\v 3 Asi imi Jehovha muri nhoo yangu kumativi ose; Kudzo yangu, nomusimudzi womusoro wangu,
\v 4 Ndinodana kuna Jehovha nezwi rangu,
\s Iye anondipindura ari pagomo rake dzvene.
\p
\v 5 Ndakavata pasi ndikabatwa nehope; Ndikamuka; nokuti Jehovha anonditsigira.
\p
\v 6 Handingatyi zviuru zvamazana zvavanhu,
\s Vakandikomberedza kuzorwa neni.
\p
\v 7 Simukai, Jehovha; ndirwirei, Mwari wangu;
\s Nokuti makarova vavengi vangu vose pashaya dzavo;
\s Makavhuna meno avakaipa.
\p
\v 8 Ruponeso runobva kuna Jehovha; Kukomborera kwenyu ngakuve
\s pamusoro pavanhu venyu.
